{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_35","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2960-library-new-request-org.apache.hadoop-hadoop-yarn-client-2.7.3-28ca34e3\n\nThe most likely failing stage was generated test verification. The earliest failing run in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T06-01-52-252451Z.log` shows `Hadoop_yarn_clientTest.sharedCacheClientComputesChecksumForLocalFile()` failing on the JVM with `UnsupportedOperationException: getSubject is not supported`, coming from `Subject.getSubject -> UserGroupInformation.getCurrentUser -> SharedCacheClientImpl.getFileChecksum`. The same failure is captured in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-09T06-08-07-111624Z.log`.\n\nA later follow-up fix was able to make the coordinate pass locally, but only after adding substantial YARN reflection metadata. `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/metadata-fix/codex.log` shows the eventual additions around `RecordFactoryPBImpl.get()`, `ChecksumSHA256Impl.<init>()`, and many guarded `api.records.impl.pb.*` / `api.protocolrecords.impl.pb.*` constructors. `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-client/2.7.3/execution-metrics.json` reports 7 iterations, 315 generated LOC, and 208 metadata entries, while `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-client/2.7.3/stats.json` reports `0/0` dynamic-access calls, so the automation had little dynamic-access signal to guide metadata generation.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T06-01-52-252451Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-09T06-08-07-111624Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `stats/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-yarn-client/2.7.3/execution-metrics.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch and decide whether to keep the `SharedCacheClient` checksum test or replace it with a less UGI-sensitive public-API test.\n2. Validate the broad YARN protobuf reflection metadata additions on the preserved branch and trim them if a narrower set is sufficient.\n3. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3` and `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-yarn-client:2.7.3` before opening a PR."}}
